HEADWORD: Escambio
<hw>Es*cam"bi*o</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>escambium</ets>, <ets>excambium</ets>. See <er>Excamb</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Eng. Law)</fld> <def>A license formerly required for the making
over a bill of exchange to another over sea.</def>
<rj><au>Cowell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
